snippet: A Los Angeles prosecutor told a judge there is little evidence that the singer Chris Brown completed the community service he was ordered to do as part of his sentence for assaulting Rihanna four years ago.
abstract: A Los Angeles prosecutor told a judge there is little evidence that the singer Chris Brown completed the community service he was ordered to do as part of his sentence for assaulting Rihanna four years ago.

headline.main: Prosecutors Ask Judge to Revoke Chris Brown’s Probation
